node.text:
What an amazing NCA Camp!  The Scots are going home with:
-Most Spirited Award
-1st Place Rally Routine
-1st Place GameDay
-Game Day Run-Off Champions
-4 All-Americans
-Top Gun Group Stunt Champions
-Best All-Around Team
-GOLD Paid Bid!

Thank you @terrellsfamous and @ncacheer camps for giving us such a great start to our season!
#TeamX #Prosper
